P(x,y,z)=yx^{3}+zx^{3}+xy^{3}+zy^{3}+xz^{3}+yz^{3}
=x^3(y+z+x-x)+y^3(x+z+y-y)+z^3(x+y+z-z)
=x^3(x+y+z)+y^3(x+y+z)+z^3(x+y+z)-x^4-y^4-z^4
=(x+y+z)(x^3+y^3+z^3)-(x^4+y^4+z^4)
